author: gstein
msg: Some basic adjustments to a couple deprecated functions.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/deprecated.c:
(svn_wc_add3): use db_read_kind() rather than the node wrapper, then
tighten the scope of ADM_ACCESS
(svn_wc_get_ancestry): rewrite in terms of internal_get_ancestry so that
we don't need a WC_CTX.

author: gstein
msg: Minor changes and tweaks
* subversion/libsvn_wc/copy.c:
(determine_copyfrom_info): remove the DST_URL and DST_REVISION
parameters. the callers can do this check themselves (and the check
and mechanism for doing so may change soon).
(copy_file_administratively): omit params to determine_copyfrom_info,
and do the check/copyfrom info reset ourself. also use the internal
get_pristine_contents() rather than the public function.
(copy_dir_administratively): use a single dirent_split, rather than two
function calls. expand the comments around the cleanup3 call. omit the
parameters to determine_copyfrom_info and do the work ourself. use
svn_error_return for the call to add4
